item.content:encoded:
• Stream.publish - Facebook Developer Wiki
    This method publishes a post into the stream on the user's or Facebook Page's Wall and News Feed. This post also appears in the streams (News Feeds) of the user's friends' or Page's fans. If you specify a target_id, then the post appears on the Wall of the target, and not the user posting the item.
    (tags: facebook api stream post php feed)
  • UrlRewritingNet.UrlRewrite - Home
    Welcome to project page of UrlRewritingNet.UrlRewrite. UrlRewritingNet.UrlRewrite is an Open Source Component for easy and reliable rewriting URLs with ASP.NET
    (tags: asp.net .net development urlrewrite urlrewriting iis url dotnet mod_rewrite utility)
